  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>General</Type>
    <Text>The hotel features a outdoor swimming pool, fitness room, beauty salon, barber and business center. Conference facilities are also available on 5th-8th floor with maximum capacity of 25-120 pax. (12/07SW)</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>SurroundingArea</Type>
    <Text>Located on the heart of Silom main road adjacent to Narai Hotel.  Transfers from the airport to the hotel takes about 30-40 minutes.  Hotel is located close to Patpong famous night bazaar, restaurants, pubs and bars as well shopping centers such as Central or Robinson Department store. The hotel is walking distance to the skytrain Chongnonsri station.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>RoomTypes</Type>
    <Text>90 Deluxe Rooms offer guests a beautiful and impressive view of the city for an unforgettable stay. With modern sleek glass, the stylishly designed interior is a veritable retreat from the hustle and bustle of city life. All accommodation features distinctive touches such as coffee and tea-making facilities, in-room safe, IDD telephone, hairdryer, local and cable television channels and broadband internet connectivity.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>PropertyInformation</Type>
    <Text>A high rise 20 storey concrete and black glass sheet building with a combination of hotel service and apartment. Parking space is available on 1th-5th floor.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>DiningFacilities</Type>
    <Text>The hotel's coffee shop is located on the 2nd floor and features an American breakfast buffet, international buffet lunch with Thai, Japanese and European food and a la carte dinner menu.  The Roof Top Beer Garden overlooks central Bangkok and has lovely views.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>Short</Type>
    <Text>New renovation. Welcoming and comfortable lobby in air condition with red sofa
seat.</Text>
  </Description>
